Dr. Constantine Wesonga has been elected as the secretary-general of the university staff association AUASU after trouncing his closest opponent Kwashe Kubasu. Dr, grace Nyongesa is the new chairperson taking over from Prof Muga Kolale. Dr. Grace Nyongesa who has been teaching at Kisii university beat Muiga Rugara from JKUAT. Onesmus Mutio becomes the union&rsquo;s new secretary while Janepher Kumba is the new treasurer. Cyprian Ombati will be the vice-chairperson, Jacob Musembi takes over as the deputy secretary-general while Weldon Keterent will the vice treasurer.